@@@@@@@Create Your Email Blueprint @@@@@@@@@ Remember, the more you put in upfront, the more Al can work for you. @@@|
1. List three adjectives to describe your
ideal communication style.

Some of my favorites are charismatic,
professional, memorable, powerful, friendly, and clear.

I recommend telling Al to minimize wordiness (not being specific, set desired length) and avoid jargon. be clear concise and avoid communication weaknesses (like like hedging or qualifying.) and play on communication strengths.
