Citing Sources: Prompts
"Cite your sources"
"Use data in your response"
"Use historical examples in your response"
"Use a hypothetical example that would be
relevant to professionals"
"Please only use academic sources"
"If you use less reputable source 
make a clear distinction for the reader."
